title: Chicago NAA OBD Test Only Vehicle Testing Stations - June 14, 2018
description: This data layer contains the locations of Chicago Non-Attainment Area OBD Test Only Vehicle Testing Station locations. To be used for ArcGIS Desktop 10.1 and ArcGIS Server 10.1 web applications using the ArcGIS Viewer for Silverlight. Also to be viewed in the Operations Dashboard and updated using the iPhone Collector App. Web Maps and Web Applications created in ArcGIS Online for Organizations.
